<%@title = "Resource Index"%>

<p style="padding:10px;margin:10px; border:1px solid #EFEFEF;" >
NCBO is building a system for automated ontology-based annotation and indexing of biomedical data. We process the textual metadata of diverse elements of biomedical resources 
such as gene expression data sets, descriptions of radiology images, clinical-trial reports, and PubMed abstracts to 
annotate and index them with terms from appropriate ontologies. Use the interface below to search the resulting index of annotations and to identify 
biomedical data resources annotated with particular ontology terms. Try searching for "Melanoma" and use NCI Thesaurus as your ontology.
</p>


